\t\u003ccite\u003eLionsgate\u003c/cite\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\tAlthough it isn’t even summer yet, it’s never to early or late to have a cozy movie night with the \u003cem\u003eTwilight \u003c/em\u003efilms. While costars Robert Pattinson and Kristen Stewart have both taken off in their careers as movie stars, it’s always fun to revisit their big breaks. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\tAll five films in the saga — which also star Billy Burke, Sarah Clarke, Justin Chon, Anna Kendrick, Taylor Lautner, Dakota Fanning, Kellan Lutzm, Nikki Reed, Ashley Greene, Jackson Rathbone, Gil Birmingham, Rachelle Lefevre, Peter Facinelli and more — are now streaming on Netflix.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\t\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eHeart Eyes\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e – May 8\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?w=300\" data-lazy-src=\"https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?w=300\" alt=\"\u0026#39;Heart Eyes\u0026#39;\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg 6048w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?resize=150,100 150w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?resize=300,200 300w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?resize=1024,681 1024w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?resize=1536,1022 1536w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?resize=2048,1363 2048w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20240706_07842.jpg?resize=630,420 630w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HE_20